I'm a little confused. Conjecture on possibilities exist but I have seen little theory. Which threads contain them? Nuclear Power, Space Travel and ways of combining the two have existed for over half a century. The science is beyond theory. It's been proven practical. Perhaps you mean theoretical methods of employing this technology and some of the suggestions in &quot;applications&quot; caught your eye.<br>
